title: 603. 10 Takeaways from Week 7
itunes:title: 603. 10 Takeaways from Week 7
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 7 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss Browns QB Baker Mayfield bringing the team back to a victory against the Bengals on his game-winning touchdown throw (1:26). Next, the trio look at Bucs QB Tom Brady's impressive performance in a win over the Raiders (3:49). Later, the guys analyze the coaching by Cardinals head coach Kliff Kingsbury as his team beat the Seahawks in overtime (13:24). To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett talk about how the Lions finally finished a game after their win against the Falcons (29:58). All that and more in this packed episode.
